{"h678f5583g881dg439cg9ccfgc467b6f609f4": ["*Fresh, sweet-smelling water gurgles gently below.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Well.html", "3fa72a2b-b2d2-d750-7221-bba4fbc38cd0"], "h5a182c8agf3ebg4651g820fgdaa622e35d3f": ["<i>Drink from the well.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Well.html", "0b207db8-328a-3654-3c2a-9246e7bc22fc"], "h80ec8166g63e9g4cd2g9656g4e0aab90c68b": ["*The warm rush of power flows through you. You feel stronger, faster - <i>better.*</i>", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Well.html", "707117b9-d2d9-1afb-3328-e351de1ab3e5"], "h23736421g0ebag445bg9787g01775db5768a": ["*A cloying rot jams in your throat. All you can taste is <i>bile.</i>*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Well.html", "7b9992a8-f48e-da73-bf11-ba146c02fc76"], "h79230be0g3225g4c1fg88fcg03d802a72494": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Well.html", "ed7d4f5c-706a-753f-0f71-75e029fff12a"], "h66c276d1g1f05g43d1g8061gf14a0137f68c": ["*A fetid smell assaults your nostrils. Dead flesh lies below - a great deal of it.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Well.html", "49b2b9de-8de7-1501-606a-d12ee4e1a111"]}